+    • Automatically finds the Common Ancestor of two branches.                  
+    • Performs a deep recursive merge of JSON objects.                          
+    • Conflict Detection: Identifies conflicts when the same path is modified   
+      differently on both branches, or when one branch modifies a path that the 
+      other branch deleted.                                                     
+ • Immutability: Uses deep cloning on all storage and retrieval operations to   
+   prevent accidental state mutation.                                           
+ • Chronological History: getHistory traverses the commit graph to return       
+   versions in the order they were created.                                     
